Bone changes and fracture risk in individuals infected with HIV.

Warriner AH(1), Mugavero MJ.

Author information:
(1)Division of Endocrinology, Metabolism, and Diabetes, University of Alabama at 
Birmingham, FOT 702, 2000 6th Avenue South, Birmingham, AL 35233-0271, USA. 
